---
import bluetexture from "../assets/blue-texture.webp";
import sc9 from "../assets/SC-09.webp";
import sc2 from "../assets/SC-02.webp";
---

<section class="grid">
  <img class="background" src={bluetexture.src} alt="dark blue sand/texture" />
  <div class="content grid gridcenter">
    <img class="img1" src={sc9.src} alt="" />
    <img class="img2" src={sc2.src} alt="" />
    <p class="p1">
      This is EDM! We aim to explore the full spectrum of electronic dance music
      and want to take you with us. Also check out the first playlist of a
      series, where we explore the member's favourite picks of the month. Find
      the link in our bio.
    </p>
    <p class="p2">
      Thank you for everyone who came to our booth during society day! Was
      amazing to see you all in person, and we can't wait to see what the future
      holds.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .background {
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    grid-column: 1/2;
    grid-row: 1/2;
    z-index: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .content {
    grid-column: 1/2;
    grid-row: 1/2;
    z-index: 10;
    margin-top: 70px;
  }
  .img1,
  .img2 {
    width: 49vw;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 150/140;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .img1 {
    grid-column: 1/2;
    grid-row: 1/2;
    justify-self: start;
  }
  .img2 {
    grid-column: 2/3;
    grid-row: 1/2;
    justify-self: end;
  }
  p {
    color: var(--yellow);
  }
  .p1 {
    grid-column: 1/3;
    grid-row: 2/3;
    margin: 20px 30px 0 5px;
  }
  .p2 {
    grid-column: 1/3;
    grid-row: 3/4;
    margin: 20px 5px 0px 30px;
    text-align: end;
  }

  @media (min-width: 700px) {
    .content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 6;
      width: 610px;
    }
    .img1,
    .img2 {
      width: 300px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .img1 {
      grid-column: 1/2;
      grid-row: 1/4;
    }
    .img2 {
      grid-column: 2/3;
      grid-row: 2/5;
    }
    .p1 {
      grid-column: 1/2;
      grid-row: 4/7;
    }
    .p2 {
      grid-column: 2/3;
      grid-row: 5/7;
    }
  }
</style>
